This paper presents a formal language and a sequence-to-sequence network for processing it, which involves learning to encode symbol structures and query them. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and systems and control (cs.SY).
